response.original_title: Inside the Dream La Première Air France
response.overview: Immerse yourself in the world's most exclusive in-flight experience. For three years, Air France has been working in total secrecy on its new La Première service, to take elegance to new heights. Let's take off into a world of French excellence and refinement, where every detail counts, to offer the highest expression of travel.
response.title: Inside the Dream La Première Air France
